      "text": "Rear Defroster Structure Description - Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "(For vehicles equipped with auto A/C, it is controlled by the auto A/C control unit. The rear defroster/mirror heater* switch is turned ON to start operation, and the operation is canceled when the rear defroster/mirror heater* switch is turned ON again or the ignition is turned to the OFF (LOCK) mode during operation. *: Cars equipped with mirror heaters"
